'The font is in bank 5 as a picture

Load "bounder_scroll.abk"

ADVANCE=1 : LETTER=23
Unpack 5 To 1 : Screen Hide 1
Screen Open 0,400,32,8,0 : Screen Display 0,,270,,270+32 : Hide : Flash Off : Get Palette 1 : Cls 0
Def Scroll 1,0,2 To 400,30,-2,0
Double Buffer : Autoback 0
'
SC$="john hardie presents............   arty scroller  ......... created in amos basic and deluxe paint four              "
SC$=Upper$(SC$)
'
Colour Back $FFF : Make Mask 

Do 
   If LETTER>=28/2-2
      W$=Mid$(SC$,ADVANCE,1) : W=Asc(W$)
      Paste Bob 360,2,W
      Inc ADVANCE : LETTER=0
      If ADVANCE>Len(SC$) : ADVANCE=1 : End If 
   End If 
   '
   Inc LETTER
   Scroll 1
   Screen Swap 
   Wait Vbl 
   Screen Copy Physic To Logic
   Exit If Inkey$>""
Loop 






